    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but some people say that focusing on nuclear is kind of a distraction because we're basically running out of time to hit our climate goals. do you think there's a way to actually solve the crisis without it, or is it pretty much inevitable that we need nuclear to make it happen?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
